nodes.text: A Force-sensitive, Dav-Wes Renno was a Jedi Master who served the Jedi Order and the Galactic Republic in the final decade of the Republic Classic era. During the Separatist Crisis, which plagued the Galactic Republic during its final decades, the former Jedi Count Dooku reemerged as a political idealist for the Confederacy of Independent Systems. Renno and Chief Librarian Jocasta Nu assisted the journalist Harris Sanseon compile data for the HoloNet News Special Feature entitled Who is Count Dooku?.
